# Media Calls

## Connect with media
```javascript
ZYNQ.peer.connect('peer-id', {
  video: true,
  audio: true,
  resolution: 720,
  fps: 30
})
```

---

## Streams
```javascript
ZYNQ.peer.on('local-stream', stream => {
  video.srcObject = stream
})

ZYNQ.peer.on('remote-stream', ({ stream }) => {
  video.srcObject = stream
})
```
